1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:09,000
Taking walks and playing games when there's sunny weather

2
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:15,000
If there's rain, they're singing songs or reading books together

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:21,000
Every day just has a way of feeling extra lucky

4
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
When you spend it with a friend, just like Bjorn and Bucky

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Just like Bjorn and Bucky!

6
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Insomnia!

7
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:48,000
Could this get any worse?

8
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:54,000
Are you kidding me?

9
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:57,000
Shh! Nobody cares who!

10
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:59,000
Go away, world!

11
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:06,000
Stop it!

12
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:18,000
Ignore it! Just ignore it!

13
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:28,000
Gotcha! Now shh! I mean it!

14
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:30,000
I mean it!

15
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:38,000
Nooo!

16
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,000
Bjorn! Bjorn! Bjorn!

17
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:50,000
Hey! It's me! Bucky!

18
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:54,000
Hey Buck! What's going on?

19
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:58,000
Oh! Morning Bjorn! I can't sleep because I've got no sleepnia!

20
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:06,000
Insomnia! That's what they call it! Go take a nap! Come back this afternoon and we'll talk about why you can't sleep or whatever then!

21
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:10,000
How am I supposed to take a nap if I can't sleep!

22
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:12,000
Well, you've got a point there!

23
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:18,000
Well, let's solve your problem together and figure out why you're having this insomnia!

24
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:22,000
To start, tell me everything you did yesterday!

25
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Yesterday? Hang on!

26
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:26,000
Uh...

27
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,000
In the morning I did some pretty important high-tech research!

28
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,000
A little light farming!

29
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:34,000
A lot of high-level brain stuff!

30
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,000
Like most days! It's pretty taxing!

31
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:40,000
Then, after lunch, some moderate to heavy farming!

32
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,000
With yoga on the side!

33
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:48,000
Then, after some advanced gravity experiments, I invented a whole new way to use a chair!

34
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:51,000
Oh! Then finally, I thought of two rhymes for the word orange!

35
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:54,000
But I didn't have anything to write them down with, so I forgot them!

36
00:02:56,000 --> 00:03:00,000
Yeah! Uh-huh! So you just played farm hero all day long!

37
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:02,000
That pretty much covers it, yes!

38
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:05,000
Well, I was gonna do more, and then I just didn't!

39
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:11,000
Well, I do know one cure for insomnia, but I left it under this big pile of firewood!

40
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,000
Can you help find it?

41
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,000
Easy McPeasy!

42
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,000
Not really seeing anything under here!

43
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:19,000
Maybe it's under this pile!

44
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,000
Or these piles!

45
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,000
Keep looking!

46
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:23,000
You're doing great, Bucky!

47
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,000
Hey! What's up? Where's your cure?

48
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,000
It's not here!

49
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:29,000
Well, that's weird! I was sure it was there!

50
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:32,000
What if it's lost in all that big, tall grass?

51
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,000
Right! So where's the lawnmower?

52
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,000
I was hoping for the kind you ride on!

53
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,000
Oh well, this will work just fine!

54
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:43,000
Still no sign of a cure!

55
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:46,000
Keep looking! It's gotta be somewhere!

56
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,000
Nothing! Nada! Squat!

57
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,000
Well...

58
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,000
Well, what?

59
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:56,000
Now that I'm remembering, that insomnia cure could have fallen from my pocket while I was planting trees!

60
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:57,000
Wanna check?

61
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,000
Please!

62
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:03,000
Is it under that log?

63
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:05,000
Or by the fence, maybe?

64
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,000
Keep looking!

65
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,000
If I look any harder, my eyes will explode!

66
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:11,000
Yeah, it's under the log!

67
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,000
Or in the hedge!

68
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:15,000
There!

69
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,000
Hey!

70
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:27,000
I definitely had it in the flower bed, maybe!

71
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,000
Or was it in the leaves?

72
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:33,000
Or the dock that isn't there yet!

73
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:36,000
And did you check the Zen rock garden?

74
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,000
Or under my dirty dishes?

75
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,000
Oh!

76
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:41,000
Where oh where could it be?

77
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:47,000
While you're checking the roof, can you install this pinwheel?

78
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,000
Nice!

79
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,000
Thanks!

80
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:50,000
So is it up there?

81
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:59,000
I can't believe we still haven't found your insomnia medicine after looking all that time!

82
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,000
It's mega extra lost!

83
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,000
Phew!

84
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,000
Phew!

85
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,000
I'm so tired!

86
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,000
I'm sleepy!

87
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:12,000
I'll get some sleep and then we can look for the insomnia cure again in the morning!

88
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,000
Why bother with that?

89
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:19,000
A hard day's work is the best cure for insomnia at night!

90
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,000
Makes sense!

91
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:25,000
Hope I can find that no sleep me a cure when I wake up!

